column5: just a quick video i put together of two whities caught on film up at nipissing this season.  3 lbs test!
Nice vid.....you need to work on your death grip though...LOL....thought you were gonna lose the first one in the hole!  Good job.....  Sinker
not used to the gap of the hut lol
atta boy steve! nice video, nice fish too!
Nice Vid... I thought you were going to lose the first one!  nice fish! when is dinner?
nice looking fish! Somebody once told me whitefish are "greasy".  I always thought they meant the meat, but after watching you grab that first one I gotta wonder!
The first video reminded me of a "Greased Pig Catching Contest"!!! LOL  Good job Steve on such light line..
Nice work!  That defines the term of the rod being 'doubled-over'!  I'm betting you were glad you put fresh line on for the trip and that whitefish have no teeth!  Whitefish are yummy!
